            . This is the jacket I took from Alford, this is my own mark upon it, I marked it some time before.</p>
               <p>Alford's defence. I picked the jacket up in the street.</p>
               <p>Bailey's defence. I had called at my master's, to tell him I could not come to work the next day, and these persons came up to me, and charged me with robbing the shop; I know nothing of the master.</p>
